data.description: Experience a tranquil lifestyle in this pristine 1-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom condo, offering an exceptional waterfront living experience. Located within the sought-after Colonial Club community, this community offers breathtaking Intracoastal Waterway views and an abundance of amenities such as resort style pool, exercise room, billiard table, library / Card room and event hall.  Immaculate and move-in ready, this condo is situated in a vibrant 55-and-up resort-style community, and its open patio provides a charming view of lush green gardens.
